{
  "stem": "15393.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I want them to work for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, when they heard that, oh, that's all right, then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, he opened that factory within the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he employed approximately 40, between 40 and 50 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't be quite precise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And my mother was one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto, she was one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they worked, they were doing the coats, those beautiful leather coats for the gestapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On one occasion, they came and told him that his people are now almost doomed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're going for a selection, and he better look for a different place and so on, because this factory will be closed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These people are going to be taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, my people will not be taken away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, they will.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, everybody shivered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody knew that the moment they're dismissed, that means going for extermination.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not to a concentration, but extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He said, sit tight and don't worry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm going to discuss the matter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in a horse and buggy, off he went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it took hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After some hours, they saw the horse and buggy, everybody shivering in their spine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Has he managed, has he not managed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I should really stand up here to show you, but this camera won't allow it, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I have to do it sitting down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the horse and buggy, he is standing up with a paper in his hand, waving to those poor people waiting there, glued by the windows, obviously, waving the paper that he got them off, that all is well.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did he do it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He bribed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like Schindler, he bribed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
